description:
Janine Wilson has joined Sasria as the Underwriting Specialist With over 15 years of experience in the Short-term Insurance Industry, her areas of expertise include Underwriting, Reinsurance, Risk Management, Mentoring and Negotiation which have seen her occupy positions like Commercial Underwriter Assistant Manager, Senior Corporate Underwriter as well as Engineering Underwriter at some of the top insurance companies in the country.  

Janine brings to the Sasria team her professional approach, logical mind and strong problem-solving skills. Coupled with her passion for Corporate Risks and pride in seeing to it that every Mega Risk is successfully underwritten from the ground up, she is going to be a valuable addition to the team.

Prenita Naidoo joined Sasria in April 2021 as the company’s Underwriting Manager and brings with her valuable experience and knowledge from working in the insurance sector for 14 years, including working with Sub-Saharan Africa markets. She has strong business and technical competencies and has demonstrated abilities to be a top performer in the roles she has occupied, including being recognised as Employee of the Year. 

Prenita’s core strength is her analytical and strategic problem-solving skills, supplemented by her love for details and the ability to work on multi-faceted tasks and projects. She possesses much needed skills in leading, mentoring, and empowering diverse groups of people and has taken that further by obtaining a coaching certificate in 2019 – Practice for Behaviour Excellence: Women as Leaders.
